title: PAX Wrestling: Greg Miller v Dan Ryckert
description:
Dirty Dan Ryckert fired the first shot with his horrible promo (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FEnnmoYKWYE), but PAX Wrestling Commissioner Greg Miller is here to put a stop to all that.

See everything Kinda Funny's doing at PAX East 2016: http://www.kindafunny.com/paxeast
